### Install and bootstrap

- `pnpm i` (Node >= 20, `pnpm@10` per root `package.json`)

### Build, test, lint

- From repo root:
  - `pnpm build` â†’ builds all packages via Turbo
  - `pnpm test` / `pnpm test-coverage`
  - `pnpm type-check`
  - `pnpm lint` / `pnpm lint-fix`
  - `pnpm fmt` / `pnpm fmt-check`

### Per-package

- Core `durable-execution`:
  - `pnpm -F durable-execution build`
  - `pnpm -F durable-execution test`
  - `pnpm -F durable-execution build-docs`

- Drizzle storage, oRPC utils, test-utils: same pattern with `-F <package>`

### Changesets and publishing

- `pnpm cs` to version locally, `pnpm cs-publish` to run lint+tests and publish
